    "tocResponse": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"></head><body><ul id=\"chapters\"><li class=\"chapter\">第一章 初出茅庐|https://books.example.test/chapter/1.html</li><li class=\"chapter\">第二章 江湖再见|https://books.example.test/chapter/2.html</li><li class=\"chapter\">第三章 恩仇了断|https://books.example.test/chapter/3.html</li></ul></body></html>",
    "chapterResponse": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"></head><body><div class=\"content\">话说天下大势，分久必合，合久必分。此乃亘古不变之理。且听老夫细细道来。</div></body></html>"
  }
}
